.Welcome to SQL Server Import and Export Wizard

This wizard helps you to create simple packages that import and export data between many popular data formats including databases, spreadsheets, and text files. The wizard can also create the destination database and the tables into which the data is inserted.

To move or copy databases and their objects from one server instance to another, cancel this wizard and use the Copy Database Wizard instead. The Copy Database Wizard is available in SQL Server Management Studio.

A large number of tables are selected for copying, and the wizard may not be able to copy all the tables in a session. Select No to go back and unselect some tables, or select Yes to attempt to copy all the currently selected tables at one time.
